        <lcInstruction class="- topic/section learningBase/lcInstruction " id="lcInstruction_e1n_dlc_yz" xtrc="lcInstruction:1;14:54" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;15:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">The DITA Learning and Training specialization was created with the reusable learning object, or RLO, approach to learning content in mind. This derived from work by learning content
                designers at <tm class="- topic/tm " tmtype="reg" xtrc="tm:1;16:47" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">Autodesk</tm>, <tm class="- topic/tm " tmtype="reg" xtrc="tm:2;16:79" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">Oracle</tm>, <tm class="- topic/tm " tmtype="reg" xtrc="tm:3;16:109" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">Cisco</tm>, and other companies. The idea is to create a collection of information objects
                that can be reused and repurposed, depending on how you need to deliver your learning content.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;18:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">A learning object is a “discrete reusable collection of content used to present and support a single learning objective.” </p>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;19:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">The Learning &amp; Training specialization implements learningObjects with the &lt;learningObject&gt; element. The &lt;learingObject&gt; element inherits its behavior from the &lt;topicref&gt;
                element. It can contain references to the standard learning topics:<ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_epx_ch5_scb" xtrc="ul:1;20:108" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/lc_working_with_learning_objects.dita">
